public void testKeyInKeystore() {     MockSecureSettings secureSettings = new MockSecureSettings().     secureSettings.setFile(WatcherField.ENCRYPTION_KEY_SETTING.getKey(), CryptoServiceTests.generateKey()).     Settings settings = Settings.builder().put(Watcher.ENCRYPT_SENSITIVE_DATA_SETTING.getKey(), true).setSecureSettings(secureSettings).build().     assertFalse(CHECK.check(createTestContext(settings, null)).isFailure()). }
